snippet.title: Atari 2600: Qbert (Q*Bert)
snippet.description:
http://www.Insert-Disk.com proudly presents "Qbert" (Q*Bert) for the Atari 2600.

Levels 1-7 played for fun.

Q*Bert is a 1982 classic arcade game. Simply stand on the cubes to change their colour to complete a matching set. Watch out for those snakes and balls though.

I have to say that i'm a fairly poor Q*Bert player but I still enjoy playing it all these years later :-)
